      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (coarse: 2.1 mm, medium: 1.1 mm, fine: 0.55 mm global element size at screw-rod interface). QoI change from medium to fine: 0.9% for stiffness, 1.3% for yield force. Richardson extrapolation applied; GCI < 1.5%. Medium mesh selected for production runs. Discretization error well controlled."
