      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of model setup, boundary conditions, and load application by a second qualified engineer.",
      "rationale": "Model setup reviewed independently by a second FEA engineer not involved in original build. Boundary conditions, contact definitions, and load application verified against ASTM F1717 test fixture geometry. No discrepancies identified. Use error adequately controlled."
