      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model (bilinear isotropic hardening for Ti-6Al-4V) validated against coupon tensile data; contact formulation appropriate for screw-rod interface.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening parameters calibrated from five Ti-6Al-4V tensile coupons (same heat as screw stock). Elastic modulus 114 GPa, yield stress 880 MPa, tangent modulus 1.2 GPa. Augmented Lagrangian contact with friction coefficient 0.15 (literature-supported for Ti-Ti interface). Model form appropriate for quasi-static compression-bending regime."
    },
