      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single compression-bending load configuration per ASTM F1717 (500 N axial pre-load, 10 mm/min crosshead displacement). Only one test condition evaluated; the requirement for multi-condition coverage is not fully met. This factor is below the required level and is a noted limitation of the current validation dataset. Accepted under risk-based rationale given medium model risk level."
