      "rationale": "FEA fixture geometry modeled from engineering drawings of the ASTM F1717 test fixture with as-built tolerances. Crosshead displacement rate converted to quasi-static assumption (inertial effects < 0.1% of peak force). Torque applied to screw-rod interface in FEA matches assembly torque specification (4.5 Nm). Equivalency confirmed by pre-test blind prediction within 5% of mean experimental result."
